*Pomislio* sam da ću dobiti dobre rezultate na testu (I thought I would get good results on the test).
*Pomislila* je da će njen san biti ostvaren (She thought her dream would come true).
*Pomisli* da je došlo vreme da se promeni (He thought the time had come to change).
*Pomislili* smo da će se situacija promeniti (We thought the situation would change).
*Pomislivši* o tome, spremao je planove za budućnost (Thinking about it, he was making plans for the future).